ude your full name, email and physical address you used when you registered with us or made a purchase from us.\r\n\r\nIf you wish to delete your account with us, you can send us an email with the subject line of DEACTIVATE to <a href=\"mailto:info@sweetbabylilly.com.au\">info@sweetbabylilly.com.au</a>. Please be sure to include your full name, email and physical address you used when you registered with us or made a purchase from us.\r\n\r\nAt your request, we will provide you with a copy of any Personal Information we hold about you, unless an exception to the <i>Privacy Act 1988</i> (Cth) applies.  Please send us an email to <a href=\"mailto:info@sweetbabylilly.com.au\">info@sweetbabylilly.com.au</a> if you would like to obtain a record of any Personal Information we hold about you.\r\n\r\n<b>Protecting Children’s Privacy</b>\r\n\r\nWe are very serious about the safety of children when they use the Internet. Our Site is not intended for or designed to attract anyone under the age of 13. Consistent with and in the spirit of the Children\'s Online Privacy Protection Act  1998 (USA), we will never intentionally or knowingly request or collect personal information on our Site from anyone under the age of 13 (or older in some jurisdictions) without prior verifiable parental consent. We encourage parents to be involved in the online activities of their children to ensure that no information is collected from a child without parental permission. If we receive actual knowledge that someone under the age of 13 is providing information on our Site, or that someone is providing information about a person under the age of 13 on our Site, we will remove all personally identifiable information about that person from our files.\r\n\r\n<b>How to make a complaint</b>\r\n\r\nIf you wish to make a complaint about the collection, use or disclosure of your Personal Information pursuant to this Privacy Policy, please contact the Privacy Officer, PO Box 64, Rozelle NSW 2039 or by email